Parameter	Meaning	Default
start	The first number in the sequence	0
stop	The number to stop before	required
step	The amount to increase (or decrease) each time	1
ğŸ” Examples
1ï¸âƒ£ range(stop) â†’ counts from 0 to stop - 1

