ğŸ§  Important notes

    range() is efficient â€” it doesnâ€™t store all numbers in memory at once; it generates them as needed.

    Thatâ€™s why you can iterate over very large ranges without using lots of memory.

âœ… Quick summary
Example	Meaning	Output
